        {
            "title": "委內瑞拉首次從美國主導的原油銷售中入賬3億美元款項",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"委內瑞拉首次從美國主導的原油銷售中入賬3億美元款項\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/78g5L2K1E3JAsVqbJISYYw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/2ba67430-f6c3-11f0-adeb-9e97978219e5\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">委內瑞拉首次從美國主導的原油銷售中入賬3億美元款項</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A7%94%E5%85%A7%E7%91%9E%E6%8B%89%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E5%BE%9E%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%BB%E5%B0%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E6%B2%B9%E9%8A%B7%E5%94%AE%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%A5%E8%B3%AC3%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E6%AC%BE%E9%A0%85-002749000.html",
