        {
            "title": "挪威財相：主權財富基金沒有理由退出美國 相信格陵蘭危機可對話解決",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 挪威財政大臣延斯·斯托爾滕貝格表示，儘管地緣政治動盪帶來了<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:跨大西洋聯盟;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/跨大西洋聯盟\">跨大西洋聯盟</a>分裂的威脅，但他認為該國規模達2.1萬億美元的主權財富基金現在沒有理由退出美國市場。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我們目前還沒有看到任何理由這樣做，」斯托爾滕貝格周三在接受彭博電視台採訪時表示，「我們在美國的存在反映了美國市場的規模。我認為這對一只非常長線的基金來說是最好的方式。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">近幾周來， 格陵蘭危機不斷升級，美國總統唐納德·川普繼續堅持美國需要獲得這個北極島嶼。這場爭端正在攪動市場，川普與歐洲國家之間相互以徵收關稅和採取反制措施進行威脅。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b0534c05-6e57-3174-aa8a-86dec34b64fd-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周二，一家丹麥養老基金表示，由於近期政治動盪和金融風險增加，將撤出美國國債。挪威主權財富基金由挪威央行投資管理公司管理，有超過50%的資產投資於美國，其中包括美國國債。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：丹麥多家養老基金近期賣出美債 擔憂信用、財政和聯儲會獨立性風險(1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">斯托爾滕貝格在瑞士達沃斯發表講話時表示，跨大西洋聯盟正處於「困難的處境」，但他指出，「北約聯盟，北美和歐洲之間的紐帶，以前也曾經受過挑戰」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他表示，相信這場危機可以通過對話解決，並呼籲北約在北極地區開展更積極的合作。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Norway’s Stoltenberg Sees No Reason for Wealth Fund to Exit US</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8C%AA%E5%A8%81%E8%B2%A1%E7%9B%B8-%E4%B8%BB%E6%AC%8A%E8%B2%A1%E5%AF%8C%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E7%90%86%E7%94%B1%E9%80%80%E5%87%BA%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B-%E7%9B%B8%E4%BF%A1%E6%A0%BC%E9%99%B5%E8%98%AD%E5%8D%B1%E6%A9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA-135318445.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-21 23:45:00",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "不同於川普的直言不諱 摩根大通CEO戴蒙稱批評歐洲時他會「更委婉」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Photographer: Krisztian Bocsi/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/p.eBb07fyV8oHBhRqka3pw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/3ee029714219180aae17b81b8807c5a1\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Photographer: Krisztian Bocsi/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 摩根大通執行長傑米·戴蒙表示，在處理美國與歐洲的分歧方面，他願意採取不同於美國總統唐納德·川普的策略，目標是增強該地區的力量，而非加劇分裂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我會更委婉地談論歐洲的弱點，」戴蒙周三在達沃斯世界經濟論壇上表示。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Photographer: Krisztian Bocsi/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.9LSqHzkzgHs0GNyP5S1gQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/b3bbec03042e08a2ba801ce0ab34cf50\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Photographer: Krisztian Bocsi/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普對歐洲政治和經濟政策直言不諱的批評激怒了歐洲領導人，他要求將格陵蘭島移交美國控制的言論更在該地區引發強烈憤慨。與華盛頓的裂痕給歐洲領導人帶來了生存性問題，使他們不知如何應對美國總統不斷變化的威脅和要求。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a72e0c44-545f-3b69-987e-be9dfb3b8c24-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">戴蒙表示，雖然美國可以作為推動該地區目標實現的合作夥伴，但必須由歐洲領導層來推動變革。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「這真的不能由美國來完成，」他說道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：歐洲因川普覬覦格陵蘭島而墮入存亡危機 內部深層裂痕暴露無遺</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Dimon Says He Would Be ‘More Polite’ in Criticizing Europe</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E6%96%BC%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B4%E8%A8%80%E4%B8%8D%E8%AB%B1-%E6%91%A9%E6%A0%B9%E5%A4%A7%E9%80%9Aceo%E6%88%B4%E8%92%99%E7%A8%B1%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E6%99%82%E4%BB%96%E6%9C%83-%E6%9B%B4%E5%A7%94%E5%A9%89-133559770.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-21 23:45:02",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "川普達沃斯演講將按原定時間進行 儘管飛機故障導致抵達延誤",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:世界經濟論壇;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/世界經濟論壇\">世界經濟論壇</a>稱，美國總統唐納德·川普在達沃斯的特別講話將按計畫進行。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">論壇方面表示，川普將於當地時間下午2點30分向全球商界和政界領袖發表講話。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">一位世界經濟論壇的發言人稱，儘管空軍一號在起飛後不久因機械故障被迫返回馬裡蘭州安德魯斯聯合基地，但上述演講安排仍然不變。川普隨後最終登上替換飛機再次起飛，但這一小插曲使他前往瑞士的行程總計延誤了兩個多小時。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：空軍一號因電路故障返航 導致川普的達沃斯之行延遲</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-67630e5c-9fd2-3de0-80a3-3d8be0d9ff49-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump’s Davos Speech to Start on Schedule Despite Flight Delay</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E9%81%94%E6%B2%83%E6%96%AF%E6%BC%94%E8%AC%9B%E5%B0%87%E6%8C%89%E5%8E%9F%E5%AE%9A%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E9%80%B2%E8%A1%8C-%E5%84%98%E7%AE%A1%E9%A3%9B%E6%A9%9F%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C%E5%B0%8E%E8%87%B4%E6%8A%B5%E9%81%94%E5%BB%B6%E8%AA%A4-112021522.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-21 20:04:36",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "貝森特稱德銀CEO致電 駁斥該行分析師歐洲投資者或拋售美資產的報告",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國財政部長貝森特表示，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:德意志銀行;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/德意志銀行\">德意志銀行</a>執行長Christian Sewing致電，駁斥該行一名分析師發布的暗示歐洲投資者可能拋售美國資產的報告。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「認為歐洲投資者會拋售美國資產的想法，僅僅來自德意志銀行的一位分析師，」貝森特周三在達沃斯舉行的世界經濟論壇上表示。「德意志銀行CEO打來電話，稱德銀不認同那份分析師報告。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">德意志銀行發言人暫未置評。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">德意志銀行全球外匯研究主管George Saravelos周日在給客戶的報告中寫道，美國總統川普因格陵蘭問題向歐洲多國政府發出關稅威脅，提出了歐洲削減美國資產持倉的可能性。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-525887a8-866b-342e-ba83-050daef9cb60-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：德銀：歐洲持有8萬億美元美國債券和股票 關稅威脅下恐將資本武器化</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Saravelos在報告中指出，歐洲是美國最大的「出借方」，歐洲各國合計持有8萬億美元的美國債券和股票，幾乎是世界其他地區總和的兩倍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「在西方聯盟的地緣經濟穩定性正遭遇根本性動搖的環境下，並不是很清楚歐洲方面為何還會願意和過去一樣繼續扮演這樣的角色，」他表示。「過去幾天的事態發展，可能進一步鼓勵美元資產的再平衡。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Bessent Says Deutsche Bank CEO Called to Dismiss Analyst Report</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%9D%E6%A3%AE%E7%89%B9%E7%A8%B1%E5%BE%B7%E9%8A%80ceo%E8%87%B4%E9%9B%BB-%E9%A7%81%E6%96%A5%E8%A9%B2%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%B8%AB%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%80%85%E6%88%96%E6%8B%8B%E5%94%AE%E7%BE%8E%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2%E7%9A%84%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-091349969.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-21 17:59:35",
